<div class="content-header">Tasks Interface</div>

<div class="content">
    The tasks interface is a JavaFX application.
</div>

<div class="content">
    The tasks application pages are accessed via a series of tabs along the top.
    The contents of each page are outlined on the Tasks Pages.
</div>

<div class="content">
    Output is sent to the scroll pane at the bottom, and can be redirected to file, if desired.
</div>

<div class="content">
    The interface has no menu, and is closed by selecting the X at the top left of the tool.
</div>

